<!-- Please describe your review or bug you found. -->
I clicked 2x fast on the start button cause my e-mail address was in the log filter box...
Which it seems started the pipeline twice in a row, which then confuses the system as the results are not going to the right location.

## Expected behaviour
<!-- What is the behaviour you expect? -->
Should either start the pipeline only once. or restart it. or update it.
## Actual behaviour
<!-- What's actually happening? -->
breaks the system
