## Long story short
When I view my files on dat-core, I only see the resource name, but not the the type (such: folder, json, csv).
That makes it hard to select the proper resource when there are multiple ones with the same name (aka subject)

## Expected behaviour
It would be helpful if it shows the resource type, as it shown on dat-core
- subjects (Folder)
- subjects (tabular, csv)
- subjects (1) (JSON)
or something similar.

## Actual behaviour
It show only the resource name. Example:
- subjects
- subjects
- subjects (1)

